gujarati.context:
Knowledge, renunciation, devotion are firm; 
Rules, duty, faith, peace of mind are the mood;
The debt from previous birth is yours, it is not our wonder.

Here are the translations:

One who does what you do, worships Him in all aspects; 
In such a virtuous one, my love is, I have not taken it on my body.

Here is the translation:

This swami thought in mind, those words were written on paper;
Then the paper was torn apart, entrusted to my dear friend Majoji with him.
